  "title": "Sales Manager (F&B/East)",
  "description": "<p>📍 Location: East </p><p>🕒 Work Hours: Monday - Friday (8.30am - 5.45pm) <br />Saturday (8.30am - 2.30pm) (1 shift every 4 weeks)</p><p>💰 Salary: Up to $6,500<br /></p><p>Our client is a leading Singapore-based professional company, known for high-performance cleaning products, offers reliable, safe, and efficient solutions designed for professional use. <br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Drive sales growth </strong>and achieve targets within the Food & Beverage and Hospitality sectors (cafes, restaurants, central kitchens, distributors, hotels, etc.).</li><li><strong>Develop new markets and key accounts </strong>through proactive prospecting and strong customer relationships.</li><li><strong>Lead and manage the sales team</strong>, including training, motivation, and performance management.</li><li><strong>Manage contracts and customer service</strong>, including negotiations, renewals, urgent deliveries, and resolving complaints.</li><li><strong>Monitor market trends and provide sales reporting</strong>, while supporting company initiatives and attending industry events as needed.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 5 years of experience in the Food & Beverage and Hospitality sector.</li><li>Proven leadership abilities.</li><li>Strong communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Possesses a Class 3 driving license and have access to a personal vehicle.</li></ul><p><br />To apply, kindly click <strong>APPLY NOW</strong> to submit your latest CV.</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br /></p><p><br /><br /><strong>SAAY</strong></p><p>EA Registration No.: R25139436</p><p>EA License No.: 25C2695</p>",
